{"tid":1512404,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"在混亂世代遺下的正義 全人類在凝視　熱切爭取的意志","createTime":"2019-08-28T01:11:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T10:18:04.000Z","uid":20209,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3a6b6340a45c5c5e7f698597f5260c67c51e843e","tid":1512404,"uid":20209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T01:11:15.000Z","msg":"像大俠勇士　延續的故事<br />\n如逃避沒意義　就更加應該試試<br />\n那管出去太艱險　讓我一試<br />\n能承受　我沒有事<br />\n理想不可減退　全力勇敢的衝出去<br />\n不死的夢裡　充斥愛和罪<br />\n重拾自信滅絕當天的畏懼<br />\n已把心魔擊退　還未留下一絲根據<br />\n彩色的烙印　天空裡凝聚<br />\n和平地戴面具　歡呼聲撐下去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"0a1e86422f027f9d55bb0e09d5ab5a75e557c4a5","tid":1512404,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T01:11:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CEqOUyf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCEqOUyf.jpg&h=2722f546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NSAWdB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNSAWdB2.jpg&h=7e1fa5a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32473e94402b703d5c30402b4b19b15a74d431a2","tid":1512404,"uid":20209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T01:16:29.000Z","msg":"大家都係幪面超人"},{"pid":"dbb29e57002c4a6fe1f931380255242b3fe05cef","tid":1512404,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T01:52:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQwwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=fd935695\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.